Hey, I'm kidding.

774
01:06:11,520 --> 01:06:16,410
Even if the overbearing CEO is unwavering, I'm still on his payroll.

775
01:06:16,410 --> 01:06:20,490
I should still prepare a small dinner.

776
01:06:21,930 --> 01:06:23,410
Why are you laughing?

777
01:06:23,410 --> 01:06:25,370
I'm just realizing now that for some people,

778
01:06:25,370 --> 01:06:27,410
you can't just listen to what they say.

779
01:06:27,410 --> 01:06:29,770
You have to look at what they do.

780
01:06:29,770 --> 01:06:31,040
What do you mean?

781
01:06:31,040 --> 01:06:33,400
I'm saying that your words are harsh, but your body language is honest.

782
01:06:33,400 --> 01:06:35,210
You're constantly criticizing Aoran with your words,

783
01:06:35,210 --> 01:06:38,960
but when it's time, you still go home to prepare dinner.

784
01:06:45,270 --> 01:06:49,030
- Zheng Xiao'en.
- What?

785
01:06:49,030 --> 01:06:52,120
Has anyone ever told you that you're very special?

786
01:06:52,770 --> 01:06:55,650
I don't think so.

787
01:06:55,650 --> 01:06:58,940
No matter which world it is, you're the first.

788
01:06:58,940 --> 01:07:04,940
I've discovered that every day, you come with different surprises.

789
01:07:07,010 --> 01:07:12,310
Are you confessing amidst the chaos?

790
01:07:13,740 --> 01:07:15,990
Hurry! Hurry up and tell me you're confessing amidst the chaos!

791
01:07:15,990 --> 01:07:19,070
This young girl's confidence needs to be mended by another hot guy.

792
01:07:19,070 --> 01:07:21,700
Cut the crap.

793
01:07:21,700 --> 01:07:23,950
You don't need me to mend it for you right now.

794
01:07:23,950 --> 01:07:27,550
I need it, I need it, I need it, I really need it.

795
01:07:27,550 --> 01:07:31,440
God, please give me a glass of overbearing CEO with no ice and 100% sugar.

796
01:07:31,440 --> 01:07:36,920
Right now, I need lots and lots and lots of sweetness.

797
01:07:59,380 --> 01:08:00,720
Just leave it.

798
01:08:00,720 --> 01:08:03,380
It's fine. I will wash the dishes.

799
01:08:10,620 --> 01:08:12,520
You need to...

800
01:08:13,110 --> 01:08:15,080
What?

801
01:08:16,050 --> 01:08:18,040
It's nothing.

802
01:08:22,700 --> 01:08:24,790
You need to change the gloves.

803
01:08:24,790 --> 01:08:27,320
Those are Zheng Xiao'en's.

804
01:08:32,250 --> 01:08:34,200
That...

805
01:08:37,540 --> 01:08:40,720
- Thank you.
- This is nothing.

806
01:08:40,720 --> 01:08:43,160
That towel hasn't been boiled.

807
01:08:43,160 --> 01:08:46,930
The ones Xiao'en boiled are hanging outside to dry.

808
01:08:52,220 --> 01:08:55,070
Someone else lives at your house?

809
01:08:55,880 --> 01:08:58,140
I'm home.

810
01:09:10,050 --> 01:09:14,990
Do you... like the CEO?

811
01:09:14,990 --> 01:09:17,780
I do. I like the CEO.

812
01:09:17,780 --> 01:09:22,390
You don't have to accept her feelings, but don't question her sincerity.

813
01:09:22,390 --> 01:09:24,560
If you don't want to see me, I'll just leave.

814
01:09:24,560 --> 01:09:26,560
When did I say that I don't want to see you anymore?

815
01:09:26,560 --> 01:09:28,490
You want to straddle two boats?

816
01:09:28,490 --> 01:09:30,450
A boat like you doesn't even catch my eye.

817
01:09:30,450 --> 01:09:32,570
The CEO's heart is already taken.

818
01:09:32,570 --> 01:09:35,110
Even if I stay here, I won't attain the CEO's love.

819
01:09:35,110 --> 01:09:37,230
You've misunderstood Zheng Xiao'en from the beginning.

820
01:09:37,230 --> 01:09:40,270
You just haven't realized it yet.

821
01:09:47,750 --> 01:09:51,070
♫ Memories wear protective coloration ♫

822
01:09:51,070 --> 01:09:54,110
♫ Ambushing in the middle of the night ♫

823
01:09:54,110 --> 01:09:59,670
♫ A quiet strike ♫

824
01:09:59,670 --> 01:10:02,790
♫ Streetlights awaiting dusk ♫

825
01:10:02,790 --> 01:10:05,110
♫ Still awaiting as always ♫

826
01:10:05,110 --> 01:10:08,200
♫ Nothing is impossible ♫

827
01:10:08,200 --> 01:10:12,660
♫ Even if no one is perfect ♫

828
01:10:12,660 --> 01:10:17,250
♫ Holding you next to my heartbeat ♫

829
01:10:17,250 --> 01:10:20,520
♫ Tightly held the palm of my hand ♫

830
01:10:20,520 --> 01:10:25,430
♫ It remains the only farewell ♫

831
01:10:25,430 --> 01:10:30,150
♫ If I could see you again ♫

832
01:10:30,150 --> 01:10:36,840
♫ Carefully planning my gamble with you ♫

833
01:10:36,840 --> 01:10:40,930
♫ In the end I lost to you ♫

834
01:10:40,930 --> 01:10:50,260
♫ I think of you until I can no longer breathe ♫

835
01:10:50,260 --> 01:10:53,940
♫ If you were a painter ♫

836
01:10:53,940 --> 01:10:55,910
♫ Then I'll be your canvas ♫

837
01:10:55,910 --> 01:11:00,210
♫ No regrets ♫

838
01:11:00,210 --> 01:11:06,410
♫ I lost all my love to you ♫
